Name: End of War 1945
About the game: End of War 1945 is an Early Access multiplayer shooter focusing on classic, dynamic gameplay in unconventional World War 2 settings. Experience non-stop action with up to 32 players, or take on bots in single player. Key Features: Up to 32 Player Matches Intense combat for matches of all sizes. 9 Maps Unique locations focused on lesser known battles set in Italy, Germany, and Yugoslavia. 3 Nations Play as Germany, the USA, and the Yugoslav Partisans. Each faction has their own arsenal of weapons to choose from. 5 Game Modes A balance of Deathmatch and nonlinear/linear objective gameplay. Full Bot Support Play with AI opponents and teammates on all game modes. Historical Authenticity Authentic weapons, uniforms, and historically immersive World War 2 setting.
